{"tid":1844532,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【快啲入黎屌左膠】旺角私了","createTime":"2020-01-26T16:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T10:56:32.000Z","uid":137109,"like":30,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"02f057abb1b83491666f3c025f3b836dd92f31f6","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"點唔會同手足割，即使係私了廢老，因為暴力根源從來都係殘暴政權。<br />\n<br />\n但要明白：<br />\n1. 始終蝕底係自己；藍絲好多時爛命一條，為咗螻蟻，值唔值你冒風險？<br />\n2. 佢唔出手，咪由佢鳩噏。佢出手、搞手足嘅，呢個係以武抗暴，值得讚揚。<br />\n3. 當佢只係鳩噏 (attention seeking)，其實唔理就係最好處理方法。<br />\n4. 你support嘅民主係用思辯改變社會，唔係用更高嘅武力令人服從；黑警已經幫你示範作<br />\n如果理念係值得支持，你要抵抗Propaganda machine去宣揚<br />\n唔係用武力改變人心，對你既理念心悅誠服。<br />\n&quot;THE STRONGEST is never strong enough to be always the master, unless he transforms strength into right, and obedience into duty.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nWinston Churchill話要打勝仗嘅話<br />\n「如果你停下來對每隻向你吠的狗扔石頭，你永遠到不了目的地。」<br />\n&quot;You will never reach your destination if you stop and throw stones at every dog that barks&quot; <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS：樓主係鬼係熱狗係離地阻膠"},{"pid":"6a7f98ccc85bb82e03020cc62700fe11974254ce","tid":1844532,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=4a631d99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"f646a1c28a747f3bb8556ccf481f038b373db4bc","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"f8b3487395707c59512be03d002c88634dcf9871","tid":1844532,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"【武漢x香港】手足聯動，五大訴求，延燒大陸！ 就蔥友和香港手足聯合發起文宣戰倡議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"263106e24b918700a1ed3d0ca7ca065c4970efd8","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"87603cddd3c6f7bcd885c7058aa57a3b5a055da1","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"8d65f65b6bb20281d9a34e17daeeecce79f5f932","tid":1844532,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"用行動消滅支那人"},{"pid":"37da6fa233e926cff795d9ae4f37e9134e736e3f","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"推 4/10<br />\n負皮入黎留言啦"},{"pid":"1eb9118a9d08d696c820aed2ba968afc53402a36","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"c59cdb87a79cc03125fde444bee23d91395c21ad","tid":1844532,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fcdf6fe18489c0f